text: Stefan Peter (born 10 April 1975) is an Austrian equestrian. He competed in the individual dressage event at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Austria Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:People from Bregenz
